  "text": "In a multicenter double-blind RCT conducted in three Danish hospitals, patients were treated with a dietary supplementation of 3.6 g of n-3 PUFAs or with fat composition as the average Danish diet. Authors described an improvement in morning stiffness and TJC at week 12 [CITATION_1] .",
